P_HTM[3271]="*appamāṇasubhā devā …**the Gods of Limitless Glory …*";
P_HTM[3272]="*subhakiṇhā devā dīghāyukā vaṇṇavanto sukhabahulāti.**the Gods Replete with Glory …*";
