P_HTM[7679]="*“Taṃ kiṃ maññasi rāhula, sotaṃ niccaṃ vā aniccaṃ vā”ti?**“What do you think, Rāhula? Is the ear …*";
P_HTM[7680]="*“Aniccaṃ, bhante … pe …* **";
P_HTM[7681]="*ghānaṃ niccaṃ vā aniccaṃ vā”ti?**nose …*";
P_HTM[7682]="*“Aniccaṃ, bhante … pe …* **";
P_HTM[7683]="*jivhā niccā vā aniccā vā”ti?**tongue …*";
P_HTM[7684]="*“Aniccā, bhante …* **";
P_HTM[7685]="*kāyo nicco vā anicco vā”ti?**body …*";
P_HTM[7686]="*“Anicco, bhante …* **";
P_HTM[7687]="*mano nicco vā anicco vā”ti?**mind permanent or impermanent?”*";
P_HTM[7688]="*“Anicco, bhante”.**“Impermanent, sir.”*";
P_HTM[7689]="*“Yaṃ panāniccaṃ dukkhaṃ vā taṃ sukhaṃ vā”ti?**“But if it’s impermanent, is it suffering or happiness?”*";
